            <who name="Daniel Wagner">daniel.wagner</who>
            <bug_when>2013-02-07 17:59:44 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>The MDoubleBorder decorator mixin wraps the decorator element in an additional div to which the outer border styles are applied. Any styles already defined on the decorator will be applied to this outer element as well, which can lead to unwanted effects such as a double shadow if the decorator also includes MBoxShadow.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
